# Astro-Strapi Hotel Booking System Rules

This is an Astro-Strapi hotel booking system with the following requirements:

## Architecture & Authentication
- Use the existing authentication flow with Django backend
- Follow the established API patterns in /api/ endpoints
- Maintain consistency with existing Tailwind component styles
- Use the Docker compose setup for all development work

## Development Guidelines
- All services must run through Docker Compose
- Frontend: Astro with React components
- CMS: Strapi for content management
- Backend: Django DRF for authentication and API
- Database: PostgreSQL with Redis for caching
- Use Yarn as the package manager for Node.js projects
- Follow the modular Docker Compose structure in /docker/ folder
